{"tid":2220270,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如真　如假　云根分身飾演自己","createTime":"2020-09-27T13:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T12:32:09.000Z","uid":343520,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f00f4a13847b6d88c8eb90d657044061b967b081","tid":2220270,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:49:30.000Z","msg":"譚詠麟<br />\n<br />\n一生中最愛（熱血公民）<br />\n<br />\n作詞：向雪懷<br />\n作曲：伍思凱<br />\n編曲：盧東尼<br />\n<br />\n云根癡癡的等某日<br />\n終於可等到香港的制憲<br />\n曾聽說泰博欠熱情<br />\n至佢倒插了國旗方知他勁型<br />\n其實～你　抗爭的一剎<br />\n會否有OT獎金？<br />\n<br />\n圖書館當天的戰役<br />\n終於只得到差佬的票控<br />\n誰發覺四眼嘅熱誠<br />\n與泰博政見貼合香港的未來<br />\n黃洋達你　領先本土派<br />\n五區要當選這一次 Ooh...<br />\n<br />\n如真　如假　云根分身飾演自己<br />\n始終香港的選民過於低智 無法了解你<br />\n<br />\n如生　如死　松泰你請珍惜自己<br />\n政黨即使分離我都想你　<br />\n我    真的想你"},{"pid":"07c1c20a14a7b0c581c34a102fe479a0aada733b","tid":2220270,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6678f33ae3a4c5611856a35a73954a29c89962a8","tid":2220270,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca52ca91eaa2d89f5cd7db952031211d6603b4f","tid":2220270,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:50:34.00